359
00:22:29,695 --> 00:22:32,960
L'anniversaire de Chandler
est avant le mien.

360
00:22:36,535 --> 00:22:38,196
Surprise !

361
00:22:41,473 --> 00:22:45,034
C'est génial !
Tous ces...

362
00:22:45,210 --> 00:22:46,199
gobelets !

363
00:22:46,378 --> 00:22:48,346
C'est bizarre.

364
00:22:48,847 --> 00:22:50,712
